      <section>
         <title>Sajáiduhttit eanet gielaid</title>

            <p>For å installere flere språk laster du ned og installerer
            selve språkfilene (såkalte zhfst-filer).</p>

            <note label="FUOM!">Beskrivelsen nedenfor gjelder ikke <a
            href="korrektur.html#Čállindárkkistanreaiddut+MS+Officii">
            retteprogrammene for MS Office</a> - der installerer man hele
            programmet for hvert språk.</note>

            <ol>
              <li>Viežžal ovtta dahje eanet zhfst-fiillaid:
                <table>
                <tr>
                  <th>Giella:</th>
                  <th>Veršuvdna</th>
                  <th>Dokumentašuvdna ja gáldokoda:</th>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td><a href="http://divvun.no/static_files/zhfsts/se.zhfst"><icon
                  alt="Download" height="44" width="44"
                  src="images/Crystal_Clear_app_download_manager.png" />
                  Davvisámegiella</a> </td>
                  <td>4.0</td>
                  <td><a href="http://giellatekno.uit.no/doc/lang/sme/index.html"
                  >Prošeaktadokumentašuvdna</a> ja <a
                  href="https://victorio.uit.no/langtech/trunk/langs/sme">gáldokoda</a>.
                  </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td><a href="http://divvun.no/static_files/zhfsts/smj.zhfst"><icon
                  alt="Download" height="44" width="44"
                  src="images/Crystal_Clear_app_download_manager.png" />
                  Julevsámegiella</a> </td>
                  <td>4.0</td>
                  <td><a href="http://giellatekno.uit.no/doc/lang/smj/index.html"
                  >Prošeaktadokumentašuvdna</a> ja <a
                  href="https://victorio.uit.no/langtech/trunk/langs/smj">gáldokoda</a>.
                  </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td><a href="http://divvun.no/static_files/zhfsts/sma.zhfst"><icon
                  alt="Download" height="44" width="44"
                  src="images/Crystal_Clear_app_download_manager.png" />
                  Lullisámegiella</a> </td>
                  <td>4.0</td>
                  <td><a href="http://giellatekno.uit.no/doc/lang/sma/index.html"
                  >Prošeaktadokumentašuvdna</a> ja  <a
                  href="https://victorio.uit.no/langtech/trunk/langs/sma">gáldokoda</a>.
                  </td>
                </tr>
                </table>
              </li>
              <li>Sirdde vižžon zhfst-fiillaid oktii dáin máhpain:
                  <ul>
                    <li>Windows: <code>&lt;User&gt;\AppData\Local\voikko\3</code><br/>
                    (≤ Windows 7: <code>C:\Documents and Settings\&lt;User&gt;\Local
                    Settings\Application Data\voikko\3</code>)</li>
                    <li>OSX: <code>~/Library/Spelling/voikko/3</code></li>
                    <li>Linux: <code>~/.voikko/3</code></li>
                  </ul>
                  Lea vejolaš sirdit zhfst-fiillaid <a
                  href="https://github.com/voikko/corevoikko/blob/master/libvoikko/README"
                  >eará máhpaide</a> jus dan háliida. Oza bajilčállaga «Search
                  order for dictionary files». Muitte ahte álo fertet bidjat
                  <code>.zhfst</code>-fiillaid máhppii man namma lea «3» daid
                  máhpaid siskkobealde man bagadus namuha.
              </li>
              <li>Olggos- ja sisačálit iežat dihtoris</li>
            </ol>

            <p>Jus dárbbašat eará gielaid go sámigielaid, de gávnnat daid <a
            href="http://divvun.org/">divvun.org</a>:s.</p>

      </section>

      <section>
         <title>Ođđa čállindárkkisteaddjit juohke beaivvi</title>

            <p>MS Office/Windows-čállindárkkisteaddjit huksejuvvojit juohke ija.
            Dat sisttisdollet gielalaš rievdademiid mat leat dahkkon dan rádjái.</p>

            <warning label="FUOM!"> Mii eat leat iskan dáid veršuvnnaid dárkilit,
            ja danne eat sáhte dáhkidit ahte dat doibmet nugo galget dahje eai
            heaitte doaibmamis. Jus šaddet váttisvuođat daiguin, váldde ođđa
            veršuvnna eret ja sajáiduhtte ođđasamos almmolaš veršuvnna fas.
            </warning>

            <p>Last ned:</p>

            <ul>
              <li><a href="http://apertium.projectjj.com/spellers/Divvun-sme-latest.msi"><icon
                  alt="Download" height="44" width="44"
                  src="images/Crystal_Clear_app_download_manager.png" />
                  Davvisámegiella</a></li>
              <li><a href="http://apertium.projectjj.com/spellers/Divvun-smj-latest.msi"><icon
                  alt="Download" height="44" width="44"
                  src="images/Crystal_Clear_app_download_manager.png" />
                  Julevsámegiella</a></li>
              <li><a href="http://apertium.projectjj.com/spellers/Divvun-sma-latest.msi"><icon
                  alt="Download" height="44" width="44"
                  src="images/Crystal_Clear_app_download_manager.png" />
                  Lullisámegiella</a></li>
            </ul>

            <p>Sáhtát ieš oaidnit guđet veršuvnnat ja gielat leat olámuttus <a
            href="http://apertium.projectjj.com/spellers/">beaivválaš ođasmahttimiid viežžanmáhpas</a>.</p>

      </section>

      <section>
         <title>Hukse iežat čállindárkkisteaddji</title>

         <note>Bagadusaid ja gohččumiid maid gávnnat vuolábealde eaktuda ahte gohččunlinnjábirrasat Macas dahje Linuxis leat oahppásat dutnje. Windowsis dát bagadusat eai dáidde doaibmat bures.</note>

         <p>Lea vejolaš hukset iežat čállindárkkisteaddji min gáldofiillain ja maid heivehit gáldofiillaid iežat dárbbuide. Daga ná:</p>

         <ol>
            <li>Čuovo bagadusaid maid gávnnat <a href="http://divvun.no/doc/infra/GettingStarted.html">dás</a> sihkkarastin dihte ahte dus leat buot prográmmat ja reaiddut maid dárbbašat.</li>

            <li>Vieččat <a href="https://sourceforge.net/projects/apertium/files/giella-core/">giella core-tarpáhka</a>, mas leat resurssat maid dárbbašat juohke gillii. Maŋŋágo viežžan lea geargan, páhkke olggos páhka sisdoalu ja čále dán terminálalásii:
                <source>
cd gtcore
./configure
make
sudo make install</source>
            </li>

            <li><!-- Last ned kildekode-tarballen for språket ditt: -->
            	Mana olggos gtcore-máhpas ja viečča iežat giela máhpa svn:s dán láhkai:
                <!--ul>
                  <li><a href="http://divvun.no/static_files/tarballs/sme.tgz">Nordsamisk</a></li>
                  <li><a href="http://divvun.no/static_files/tarballs/smj.tgz">Lulesamisk</a></li>
                  <li><a href="http://divvun.no/static_files/tarballs/sma.tgz">Sørsamisk</a></li>
                </ul-->
                <source>
svn co https://gtsvn.uit.no/langtech/trunk/langs/sme  # Davvisámegiela
svn co https://gtsvn.uit.no/langtech/trunk/langs/smj  # Julevsámegiela
svn co https://gtsvn.uit.no/langtech/trunk/langs/sma  # Lullisámegiella</source>
            </li>
            <li>Vuoje dáid gohččumiid terminálaláses:
                <source>
cd YOURLANGUAGE
./configure --with-hfst --enable-spellers
make
sudo make install</source>
                <p><code>YOURLANGUAGE</code> lea sme, smj dahje sma maid easka leat viežžan.</p>

            </li>
         </ol>
      </section>

